%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22RSS%2C%20BJP%2C%20Cops%2C%20'Common%20Muslims'%20Can't%20Be%20Blamed%20for%20Moradabad%20Riots%3A%20Judicial%20Commission%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09111302%2FF26rFrQbsAA7_5P.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20submitted%20a%20judicial%20commission%20report%20on%20the%20Moradabad%20riots%20of%201980-81%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20the%20local%20government%20could%20not%20be%20held%20responsible%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20claimed%20that%20the%20violence%20which%20killed%20at%20least%2083%20people%20and%20led%20to%20injuries%20in%20112%20others%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpre-planned%E2%80%9D%20by%20local%20Muslim%20leaders%2C%20reports%20on%20various%20news%20outlets%20have%20said.%20%E2%80%9CCommon%20Muslims%E2%80%9D%20were%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20violence%2C%20it%20said%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmoradabad-riot-report-uttar-pradesh-assembly-rss-8883134%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Moradabad%20riots%20began%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Eid-ul-Fitr%2C%20August%2013%2C%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20city%20in%201980%20and%20lasted%20until%20January%201981.%20The%20violence%20spread%20to%20Aligarh%2C%20Bareilly%20and%20Allahabad%20(now%20named%20Prayagraj).%20It%20was%20considered%20then%20the%20first%20big%20communal%20clash%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20since%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Freport-clears-rss-and-bjp-of-wrongdoing-in-moradabad-riots-blames-muslim-political-leaders-instead-101691520906005.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20no%20government%20has%20made%20the%20report%20submitted%20by%20a%20one-man%20inquiry%20commission%20led%20by%20former%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20M.P.%20Saxena%20in%201983%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20458-page%20report%20was%20tabled%20by%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20in%20the%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20on%20August%208%2C%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20government%20officer%2C%20employee%20or%20Hindu%20was%20responsible%20for%20fomenting%20trouble%20at%20Eidgah%20or%20other%20places.%20The%20RSS%20or%20the%20BJP%20nowhere%20came%20on%20the%20front%20in%20these%20riots.%20Even%20common%20Muslims%20were%20not%20responsible%20for%20violence.%20This%20was%20a%20handiwork%20of%20Muslim%20League%20led%20by%20Shamim%20Ahmad%20and%20Hamid%20Hussain%20alias%20Ajji%20and%20their%20supporters.%20The%20riots%20were%20pre-planned%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20blames%20the%20political%20ambitions%20of%20Dr%20Shamim%20Ahmed%20Khan%2C%20who%20revived%20the%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20pins%20the%20beginnings%20of%20the%20violence%20to%20rumours%20being%20spread%20about%20pigs%20being%20set%20loose%20among%20those%20offering%20namaz%20at%20the%20Eidgah%20in%20Moradabad.%20Word%20also%20went%20around%20that%20Muslims%2C%20including%20children%2C%20were%20being%20killed.%20This%20incited%20violence%20and%20counter-violence%20among%20religious%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20even%20though%20most%20were%20killed%20in%20stampedes%2C%20the%20sentiment%20spreading%20on%20the%20ground%20was%20that%20people%20were%20being%20killed%20by%20members%20of%20other%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691559868000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F0911130