lice%20responsible%20for%20allowing%20violence%20against%20them%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20has%20faced%20anger%20in%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20Valley%20areas%20for%20allegedly%20supporting%20Kuki%20militant%20groups.%C2%A0The%20Manipur%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20even%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20must%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20state%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20general%20public%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BJP%20unit%20demanded%20that%20they%20be%20replaced%20by%20%E2%80%9Cany%20other%20paramilitary%20forces%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691558458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095357%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.01-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20video%20of%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Bishnupur%20police%20had%20earlier%20gone%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%20issue%20warnings%20as%20storm%20Khanun%20moves%20north%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691558210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102561119%2Cimgsize-1919653.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-south-korea-issue-warnings-as-storm-khanun-moves-north%2Farticleshow%2F102560715.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.i