r-crossing-from-turkey%2Famp_articleshow%2F102560378.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fthe-un-announces-that-a-deal-has-been-reached-with-syria-to-reopen-border-crossing-from-turkey%2Famp_articleshow%2F102560378.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Did%20Not%20Start%20Lok%20Sabha%20Debate%20On%20No-Trust%20Vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20gear%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-trust-motion-lok-sabha-bjp-congress-india-narendra-modi-rahul-gandhi-manipur-violence-no-confidence-debate-to-resume-in-parliament-today-10-points-4281677%5C%22%3EDay%202%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20all%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20address%20the%20House%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearing%20the%20air%20on%20when%20Mr%20Gandhi%20will%20speak%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20will%20speak%20today.%20He%20will%20begin%20from%20our%20side%20at%20noon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20reports%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20would%20start%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20backed%20by%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA.%20The%20motion%20was%20moved%20by%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20Kaliabor%20MP%20and%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20but%20the%20reports%20said%20he%20would%20step%20aside%20to%20let%20Mr%20Gandhi%20initiate%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20the%20House%20met%20yesterday%2C%20it%20was%20Mr%20Gogoi%20who%20started%20the%20debate.%20The%20treasury%20benches%20did%20not%20lose%20the%20opportunity%20to%20take%20a%20swipe%2C%20with%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20come%20to%20hear%20him%20(Mr%20Gandhi)%20speak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20responded%20that%20whatever%20is%20discussed%20in%20the%20Speaker's%20chamber%20stays%20there.%20He%20questioned%20if%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20if%20he%20cited%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20remarks%20in%20the%20chamber.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20MPs%2C%20led%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20dared%20him%20to%20speak%20out.%20The%20chaos%20continued%20before%20Mr%20Gogoi%20eventually%20started%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Congress%20sources%2C%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20let%20Mr%20Gogoi%20begin%20the%20debate%20primarily%20due%20to%20two%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20Mr%20Gogoi%20is%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20Northeast%20region%20and%20his%20beginning%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-trust%20motion%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20holds%20a%20symbolic%20significance.%20Also%2C%20replacing%20him%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20is%20back%20as%20an%20MP%20would%20only%20expose%20the%20party%20to%20attacks%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20never%20loses%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20the%20dynasty%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20reason%20of%20not%20fielding%20Mr%20Gandhi%20on%20Day%201%20of%20the%20debate%20was%20the%20absence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20the%20House.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20likely%20to%20speak%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20tomorrow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20are%20well%20aware%20that%20they%20do%20not%20stand%20a%20chance%20in%20this%20no-confidence%20motion%20as%20far%20as%20numbers%20are%20concerned.%20The%20move%20is%20primarily%20to%20force%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20address%20the%20House%20on%20Manipur%20and%20target%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%20The%20party%2C%20therefore%2C%20does%20not%20want%20to%20provide%20any%20opportunity%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20turn%20the%20situation%20to%20its%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20Mr%20Chowdhury's%20confirmation%2C%20there%20was%20confusion%20regarding%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20Lok%20Sabha%20address.%20While%20some%20sources%20in%20the%20Congress%20had%20been%20saying%20he%20may%20speak%20today%2C%20reports%20said%20he%20is%20scheduled%20to%20attend%20a%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20is%20back%20as%20an%20MP%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stayed%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20criminal%20defamation%20case%20over%20the%20'Modi%20surname'%20remark.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691557560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fu6bhu8go_rahul-gandhi_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-prime-minister-narendra-modi-parliament-live-no-trust-debate-no-confidence-motion-when-will-rahul-gandhi-speak-big-question-as-no-trust-d-4281768%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20gear%20up%20for%20Day%202%20of%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20all%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20address%20the%20House%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-prime-minister-narendra-modi-parliament-live-no-trust-debate-no-confidence-motion-when-will-rahul-gandhi-speak-big-question-as-no-trust-d-4281768%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-prime-minister-narendra-modi-parliament-live-no-trust-debate-no-confidence-motion-when-will-rahul-gandhi-speak-big-question-as-no-trust-d-4281768%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-prime-minister-narendra-modi-parliament-live-no-trust-debate-no-confidence-motion-when-will-rahul-gandhi-speak-big-question-as-no-trust-d-4281768%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20To%20Speak%20Today%2C%20No-Trust%20Motion%20Debate%20Enters%20Day%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20reinstated%20in%20parliament%20yesterday%2C%20will%20open%20the%20Opposition%20debate%20on%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20moved%20by%20the%20Congress%C2%A0against%20the%20BJP-led%20Central%20government%2C%20said%20party%C2%A0leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Opposition%2C%20which%20has%20brought%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20despite%20lacking%20in%20numbers%2C%20admitted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20method%20to%20compel%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20speak%20on%20Manipur%2C%20which%20has%20dominated%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20reply%20to%20the%20debate%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20chaired%20the%20BJP's%20Parliamentary%20Party%20meeting%20yesterday%20ahead%20of%20the%20big%20vote.%20Taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20reportedly%20said%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20vote%20to%20express%20distrust%20in%20the%20government%2C%20but%20to%20see%20who%20can%20trust%20whom%20in%20the%20opposition.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20test%20of%20their%20own%20internal%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reportedly%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20frequently%20attacked%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20for%20calling%20itself%20INDIA%2C%20accusing%20the%20parties%2C%20particularly%20the%20Congress%2C%20of%20attempting%20a%20rebranding%20to%20whitewash%20their%20past%20record%20as%20the%20former%20UPA%20or%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUnion%20Ministers%20-%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20and%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20speak%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%C2%A0Kiren%20Rijiju%2C%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20debate%20yesterday%2C%20said%20the%20Opposition%20will%20regret%20bringing%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20because%20it%20comes%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20time%20and%20the%20wrong%20manner%26quot%3B%2C%20given%20India's%20current%20stature%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20debate%20was%20initiated%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20said%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20was%20forced%20to%20bring%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20against%20the%20government%20to%20break%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bvow%20of%20silence%26quot%3B%20on%20Manipur.%20He%20alleged%20that%20a%20government%20which%20talks%20about%20%26quot%3Bone%20India%26quot%3B%20has%20created%20%26quot%3Btwo%20Manipurs%20--%20one%20living%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20valley%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%C2%A0during%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20bill%20on%20Monday%2C%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20of%20running%20away%20from%20a%20debate%20on%20Manipur.%20%26quot%3BThe%20question%20is%20Manipur%20situation%20and%20what%20steps%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20there%2C%20not%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20by%20voting.%20If%20you%20want%20voting%2C%20I%20dare%20you%20to%20make%20this%20bill%20fall%20through%20voting%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20session%2C%20which%20started%20on%20July%2020%2C%20has%20been%20continually%20disrupted%20by%20Opposition%20protests.%20The%20opposition%20contends%20that%20in%20view%20of%20the%20170-plus%20deaths%2C%20injuries%20and%20displacements%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20since%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20May%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20urgent%20that%20can%20demand%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20attention.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20has%20argued%20that%20after%20major%20violence%20took%20place%20in%20Manipur%20in%201993%20and%201997%2C%20no%20statement%20was%20made%20in%20the%20Parliament%20in%20one%20case%20and%20in%20the%20other%2C%20the%20junior%20home%20minister%20had%20given%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20currently%20has%20539%20members%20who%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20motion%2C%20of%20which%20the%20majority%20mark%20will%20be%20270.%20The%20BJP%20alone%20has%20301%2C%20while%20its%20allies%20have%20had%2031%20more%20votes.%C2%A0The%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20143%20while%20parties%20like%20KCR's%20BRS%2C%20YS%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20YSRCP%2C%20and%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20BJD%20have%20a%20combined%20strength%20of%2070.%20YSRCP%20(22)%20and%20BJD%20(12)%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20back%20the%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691557500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fuik542t8_notrust-debate_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-trust-motion-lok-sabha-bjp-congress-india-narendra-modi-rahul-gandhi-manipur-violence-no-confidence-debate-to-resume-in-parliament-today-10-points-4281677%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20are%20likely%20to%20speak%20in%20parliament%20today%20as%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20over%20Manipur%20crisis%20enters%20Day%202.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-trust-motion-lok-sabha-bjp-congress-india-narendra-modi-rahul-gandhi-manipur-violence-no-confidence-debate-to-resume-in-parliament-today-10-points-4281677%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-trust-motion-lok-sabha-bjp-congress-india-narendra-modi-rahul-gandhi-manipur-violence-no-confidence-debate-to-resume-in-parliament-today-10-points-4281677%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2