ndy-and-dry-in-hawaii-strong-gusts-complicate-wildfires-and-prompt-evacuations%2Famp_articleshow%2F102560202.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2235%2B%20People%20Attempted%20Self-Immolation%20Outside%20UP%20Govt%2C%20BJP%20Offices%20Since%20Adityanath%20Was%20Elected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09102017%2F3.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMere%20bhaiya%20ko%20maar%20diya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(My%20brother%20was%20killed)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20cried%20in%20anguish%20as%20bystanders%20and%20police%20guards%20grabbed%20her%20arms%20before%20she%20could%20set%20herself%20ablaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Baghpat%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20(August%208)%20tried%20to%20self-immolate%20outside%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20building%2C%20alleging%20police%20inaction%20in%20the%20case%20of%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20death%20under%20suspicious%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20action%20has%20been%20taken.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20four%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20woman%20was%20heard%20saying%20in%20a%20video%20of%20the%20incident.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20a%20police%20constable%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20a%20canal%20days%20after%20he%20went%20missing%20from%20home.%20She%20accused%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20in-laws%20of%20murdering%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20police%20is%20still%20awaited%2C%20according%20to%20written%20data%20shared%20by%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20himself%2C%20ever%20since%20he%20came%20to%20power%20in%20March%202017%20and%20till%20December%2031%2C%202022%2C%2035%20persons%20attempted%20self-immolation%20outside%20the%20UP%20assembly%2C%20Lok%20Bhawan%20(secretariat)%20or%20the%20state%20BJP%20headquarters.%20The%20three%20buildings%20are%20close%20to%20each%20other%20on%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20Marg%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20where%20aggrieved%20people%20and%20groups%20have%20traditionally%20come%20to%20register%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20arrangements%20on%20the%20VVIP%20stretch%20have%20been%20exposed%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20as%20individuals%20as%20well%20as%20families%20have%20turned%20up%20there%20to%20attempt%20self-immolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20UP%20assembly%20monsoon%20session%2C%20Adityanath%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20on%20August%207%20said%20that%20while%2035%20persons%20have%20attempted%20self-immolation%20since%202017%2C%20four%20have%20died.%20This%20includes%20two%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%E2%80%99s%20reply%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLA%20Tufani%20Saroj%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20the%20government%20would%20take%20action%20against%20people%20who%20allegedly%20instigated%20the%20aggrieved%20persons%20to%20set%20themselves%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20home%20department%20portfolio%20which%20is%20concerned%20with%20law%20and%20order%2C%20said%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20taking%20further%20action%20as%20police%20had%20already%20filed%20FIRs%20under%20the%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20section%20in%20the%20cases%20and%20submitted%20chargesheets%20in%20courts.%20A%20total%20of%20nine%20persons%20were%20arrested%20in%20four%20separate%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20persons%20who%20died%20in%20self-immolation%20incidents%20outside%20the%20UP%20assembly%20or%20the%20BJP%20state%20headquarters%20were%20Safiya%20of%20Amethi%2C%20Anjali%20Tiwari%20of%20Maharajganj%2C%20Balram%20Tiwari%20of%20Lucknow%20and%20Surendra%20Chakraborty%20of%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20data%20shared%20by%20Adityanath%20was%20till%20December%202022%2C%20the%20figure%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20higher%20as%20of%20today.%20The%20spate%20of%20self-immolation%20attempts%20became%20a%20cause%20of%20concern%20for%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20image%2C%20and%20to%20prevent%20such%20incidents%20security%20outside%20the%20state%20assembly%20was%20beefed%20up.%20Going%20a%20step%20further%2C%20the%20government%20also%20built%20watch%20towers%20and%20equipped%20the%20police%20on%20duty%20with%20blankets%2C%20sand%20buckets%20and%20fire%20extinguishers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Unnao%20along%20with%20his%20family%20attempted%20self-immolation%20outside%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20police%20failed%20to%20take%20action%20against%20men%20accused%20by%20him%20in%20a%20complaint%20of%20attempting%20to%20sexually%20assault%20his%20two%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESafiya%2C%20aged%2050%2C%20died%20of%20burn%20injuries%20in%20July%202020%20after%20she%20along%20with%20her%20daughter%20set%20themselves%20on%20fire%20outside%20the%20UP%20secretariat.%20Police%20said%20Safiya%20had%20a%20dispute%20with%20her%20neighbour%20over%20a%20drain.%20Police%20had%20then%20arrested%20an%20AIMIM%20member%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Anoop%20Patel%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20instigating%20the%20two%20to%20self-immolate%20before%20the%20UP%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202020%2C%20Anjali%20Tiwari%2C%20in%20her%2030s%2C%20died%20after%20she%20set%20herself%20on%20fire%20alleging%20harassment%20by%20her%20in-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20month%2C%20Surendra%20Chakraborty%20died%20of%20burn%20injuries%20after%20he%20set%20himself%20on%20fire.%20The%20man%20allegedly%20committed%20the%20act%20to%20thwart%20his%20landlord%20%E2%80%98s%20attempts%20to%20evict%20him.%20A%20journalist%20who%20filmed%20the%20incident%20was%20made%20a%20co-accused%20in%20the%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20case%20on%20charges%20of%20inducing%20the%20man%20to%20self-immolate%20and%20apply%20pressure%20on%20the%20landlord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%2C%20while%20rejecting%20the%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20bail%20petition%2C%20said%20that%20a%20journalist%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20dramatise%20a%20sensational%20and%20horrifying%20incident%20and%20make%20news%20by%20putting%20his%20actor%20in%20pitiable%3Cbr%3E%5Cncondition%20in%20danger%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Balram%20Tiwari%2C%20aged%2050%2C%20died%20after%20he%20self-immolated%20outside%20the%20BJP%20office%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20accusing%20his%20landlord%20of%20harassment%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691556673000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09102017%2F3.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F35-people-attempted-self-immolation-outside-up-govt-bjp-offices-since-adityanath-was-elected%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20of%20those%20attempting%20self-immolation%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20authorities%20have%20ignored%20their%20plight%20and%20complaints%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20take%20this%20step.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F35-people-attempted-self-immolation-outside-up-govt-bjp-offices-since-adityanath-was-elected%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beethoven's%20Hair%20DNA%20Reveals%20Information%20That%20The%20World%20Doesn't%20Know%20Yet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERoughly%20two%20centuries%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Ludwig%20van%20Beethoven%2C%20genetic%20examinations%20were%20performed%20on%20hair%20strands%20attributed%20to%20the%20renowned%20German%20composer.%20These%20analyses%20unveiled%20new%20revelations%20pertaining%20to%20his%20health%20challenges%2C%20hearing%20impairment%2C%20and%20ancestral%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20year%201802%2C%20Ludwig%20van%20Beethoven%20tasked%20his%20siblings%20with%20the%20request%20that%20his%20physician%20communicate%20to%20the%20public%20about%20his%20condition%E2%80%94his%20gradual%20loss%20of%20hearing%E2%80%94once%20he%20was%20dead.%20He%20hoped%20that%20this%20disclosure%20would%20help%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20sense%20of%20understanding%20and%20acceptance%20from%20the%20world%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20researchers%20have%20partially%20achieved%20their%20goal%20by%20examining%20DNA%20extracted%20from%20his%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20primary%20goal%20was%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20Beethoven's%20health%20problems%2C%20which%20famously%20include%20progressive%20hearing%20loss%2C%20beginning%20in%20his%20mid-%20to%20late-20s%20and%20eventually%20leading%20to%20him%20being%20functionally%20deaf%20by%201818%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Johannes%20Krause%20from%20the%20Max%20Planck%20Institute%20for%20Evolutionary%20Anthropology%20in%20Leipzig%2C%20Germany.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ecl21an%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fecl21an_the-moscheles-lock_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20frame%20containing%20a%20lock%20of%20hair%20attributed%20to%20Beethoven%20was%20cut%20from%20his%20head%20by%20Anton%20Felix%20Schindler%20on%20March%2024%2C%201827%2C%20and%20given%20to%20Ignaz%20Moscheles%20after%20Beethoven's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20unable%20to%20find%20a%20definitive%20cause%20for%20Beethoven's%20deafness%20or%20gastrointestinal%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Krause%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20did%20discover%20a%20number%20of%20significant%20genetic%20risk%20factors%20for%20liver%20disease.%20We%20also%20found%20evidence%20of%20an%20infection%20with%20the%20hepatitis%20B%20virus%20in%20the%20months%20before%20the%20composer's%20final%20illness.%20Those%20likely%20contributed%20to%20his%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Current%20Biology%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20commonly%20happens%20when%20people%20analyze%20DNA%2C%20the%20researchers%20uncovered%20another%20surprise.%20Beethoven's%20Y%20chromosome%20doesn't%20match%20that%20of%20any%20of%20five%20modern-day%20relatives%20carrying%20the%20same%20last%20name%20and%20sharing%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20genealogical%20records%2C%20a%20common%20ancestor%20with%20Beethoven's%20paternal%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20finding%20points%20to%20an%20extramarital%20%26quot%3Bevent%26quot%3B%20somewhere%20over%20the%20generations%20on%20Beethoven's%20father's%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20authors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20finding%20suggests%20an%20extrapair%20paternity%20event%20in%20his%20paternal%20line%20between%20the%20conception%20of%20Hendrik%20van%20Beethoven%20in%20Kampenhout%2C%20Belgium%2C%20in%20c.%201572%20and%20the%20conception%20of%20Ludwig%20van%20Beethoven%20seven%20generations%20later%2C%20in%201770%2C%20in%20Bonn%2C%20Germany%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tristan%20Begg%2C%20now%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691556600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fblj5mkg_ludwig-van-beethoven_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fbeethovens-hair-dna-reveals-information-that-the-world-doesnt-know-yet-4281890%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20his%20death%2C%20researchers%20have%20diligently%20worked%20to%20reconstruct%20Beethoven's%20medical%20past%2C%20presenting%20a%20range%20of%20potential%20reasons%20for%20his%20numerous%20health%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fbeethovens-hair-dna-reveals-information-that-the-world-doesnt-know-yet-4281890%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fbeethovens-hair-dna-reveals-information-that-the-world-does