.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhyderabad-accident-he-went-to-terrace-on-midnight-date-fell-to-death-hiding-from-girls-father-4281692%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhyderabad-accident-he-went-to-terrace-on-midnight-date-fell-to-death-hiding-from-girls-father-4281692%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhyderabad-accident-he-went-to-terrace-on-midnight-date-fell-to-death-hiding-from-girls-father-4281692%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Election%20Commission%20Disqualifies%20Imran%20Khan%20for%205%20Years%20After%20Conviction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F10141826%2FScreenshot-2023-05-10-at-2.17.56-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20on%20Tuesday%20(August%208)%20disqualified%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan%20from%20holding%20public%20office%20for%20five%20years%20after%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trial%20court%20in%20Islamabad%20had%20on%20Saturday%20sentenced%20Khan%20to%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20imprisonment%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Pakistani%20Rs%20100%2C000%20for%20allegedly%20concealing%20details%20of%20toshakhana%20gifts.%20The%20sentence%20and%20fine%20are%20the%20maximum%20penalty%20provided%20by%20Section%20174%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Election%20Act.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20cheated%20while%20providing%20information%20of%20gifts%20he%20obtained%20from%20Toshakhana%20which%20later%20proved%20to%20be%20false%20and%20inaccurate.%20His%20dishonesty%20has%20been%20established%20beyond%20doubt%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20order%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-imran-khan-arrested-guilty-corrupt-practices%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after%20his%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20assumed%20office%20in%202018%20and%20was%20ousted%20in%20a%20no-confidence%20vote%20in%20April%202022.%C2%A0The%20former%20prime%20minister%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%2C%20has%20denied%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notification%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20ECP%20cited%20the%20court%20order%20and%20declared%20that%20Khan%20had%20been%20disqualified%20under%20Article%2063(1)(h)%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20Constitution%20read%20with%20Section%20232%20of%20the%20Elections%20Act%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20Mr%20Imran%20Ahmed%20Khan%20Niazi%20is%20disqualified%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20and%20is%20also%20de-notified%20as%20a%20returned%20candidate%20from%20constituency%20NA-45%20Kurram-I%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20notification%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769083%2Fecp-disqualifies-former-pm-imran-for-five-years%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20has%20said%20it%20rejects%20the%20notification%20for%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20disqualification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20legal%20team%20has%20challenged%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20and%20the%20case%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20up%20for%20hearing%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691555758000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F10141826%2FScreenshot-2023-05-10-at-2.17.56-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-commission-disqualifies-imran-khan-for-5-years-after-conviction%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20trial%20court%20in%20Islamabad%20had%20on%20Saturday%20sentenced%20Khan%20to%20three%20years'%20imprisonment%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Pakistani%20Rs%20100%2C000%20for%20allege