0financiers%20-%20in%20no%20small%20part%20because%20his%20multibillion-dollar%20business%2C%20the%20Shriram%20Group%2C%20has%20thrived%20in%20an%20industry%20that%20tripped%20up%20countless%20others%20around%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ajcalp2%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fajcalp2_r-thyagarajan-bloomberg_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER%20Thyagarajan%2C%20founder%20of%20Shriram%20Group%2C%20at%20the%20company's%20office%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pioneer%20in%20extending%20credit%20to%20India's%20poor%20for%20trucks%2C%20tractors%20and%20other%20vehicles%2C%20Thyagarajan%20built%20Shriram%20into%20a%20conglomerate%20that%20employs%20108%2C000%20people%20in%20everything%20from%20insurance%20to%20stockbroking.%20Shares%20of%20the%20group's%20flagship%20firm%20hit%20a%20record%20in%20July%20after%20jumping%20more%20than%2035%25%20this%20year%2C%20four%20times%20more%20than%20India's%20benchmark%20stock%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2086%2C%20and%20settled%20into%20an%20advisory%20role%2C%20Thyagarajan%20said%20in%20a%20rare%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20News%20that%20he%20entered%20the%20industry%20to%20prove%20lending%20to%20people%20without%20credit%20histories%20or%20regular%20incomes%20isn't%20as%20risky%20as%20it's%20perceived.%20He%20insists%20there's%20nothing%20unusual%20about%20his%20approach%20to%20business%20-%20or%20his%20decision%20to%20give%20away%20a%20stake%20in%20Shriram%20now%20valued%20at%20more%20than%20%24750%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20leftist%2C%26quot%3B%20RT%2C%20as%20he's%20known%2C%20said%20in%20the%20south%20Indian%20city%20of%20Chennai%2C%20where%20he%20founded%20the%20group%20in%201974.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20never%20enthusiastic%20about%20making%20life%20pleasanter%20for%20people%20who%20already%20have%20a%20good%20life.%26quot%3B%20Rather%2C%20I%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20take%20away%20some%20unpleasantness%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20who%20are%20getting%20into%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThyagarajan's%20career%20highlights%20untapped%20opportunities%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country%2C%20as%20more%20of%20its%201.4%20billion%20people%20strive%20to%20enter%20a%20growing%20middle%20class.%20Though%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20has%20pushed%20to%20expand%20access%20to%20India's%20banking%20services%2C%20about%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20nation%20still%20doesn't%20have%20access%20to%20the%20formal%20financial%20system.%20And%20roughly%20a%20third%20of%20those%20who%20do%20have%20a%20bank%20account%20never%20use%20it%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Bank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELending%20to%20the%20poor%20is%20a%20form%20of%20socialism%2C%20Thyagarajan%20contends.%20But%20by%20offering%20a%20cheaper%20option%20than%20the%20punitive%20rates%20available%20to%20the%20unbanked%2C%20he%20has%20sought%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20business%20can%20be%20safe%20and%20profitable.%20And%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20he's%20persuaded%20other%20companies%20to%20bring%20down%20borrowing%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20big%20business.%20India%20has%20about%209%2C400%20so-called%20shadow%20banks%2C%20which%20mostly%20offer%20financial%20services%20to%20people%20passed%20over%20by%20conventional%20lenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRT%20is%20an%20outlier%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Srinivas%20Balasubramanian%2C%20senior%20partner%20and%20head%20of%20corporate%20finance%20at%20KPMG%20India.%20%26quot%3BFew%20have%20sustained%20and%20thrived%20for%20so%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20An%20Empire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Thyagarajan%20stands%20out%20in%20an%20industry%20that%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20ethical%20challenges%20and%20is%20prone%20to%20booms%20and%20busts%20-%20with%20blowups%20sometimes%20threatening%20the%20financial%20system.%20The%20most%20obvious%20example%20is%20the%20subprime%20mortgage%20crisis%20in%20the%20US.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20non-bank%20lender%20in%20Mexico%20last%20year%20wiped%20out%20billions%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForging%20a%20socialism-inspired%20lending%20firm%20might%20seem%20an%20unexpected%20career%20choice%20for%20a%20man%20who%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20servants%20in%20a%20well-to-do%20farming%20family%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20But%20Thyagarajan%20said%20he's%20always%20had%20an%20analytical%20and%20egalitarian-oriented%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20studied%20mathematics%20at%20the%20undergraduate%20and%20master's%20level%20in%20Chennai%20before%20spending%20three%20years%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Indian%20Statistical%20Institute%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201961%2C%20he%20joined%20New%20India%20Assurance%20Co.%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20largest%20insurers%2C%20starting%20a%20spell%20in%20finance%20as%20a%20company%20employee%20that%20lasted%20two%20decades.%20It%20included%20stints%20at%20Vysya%20Bank%2C%20a%20regional%20lender%2C%20and%20JB%20Boda%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20a%20reinsurance%20broker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%228dvse4hg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F8dvse4hg_shriram-office-bloomberg_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER%20Thyagarajan%20built%20Shriram%20into%20a%20conglomerate%20that%20employs%20108%2C000%20people%20in%20everything%20from%20insurance%20to%20stockbroking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20people%20in%20Chennai%20came%20to%20him%20seeking%20money%20to%20buy%20used%20trucks%2C%20and%20he%20gave%20them%20loans%20from%20his%20inheritance.%20Gradually%2C%20that%20side%20venture%20morphed%20into%20his%20life's%20main%20act.%20At%2037%2C%20he%20founded%20Shriram%20Chits%20with%20friends%20and%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unbanked%20often%20rely%20on%20so-called%20chit%20funds%2C%20a%20collective%20savings%20scheme%20where%20each%20member%20deposits%20a%20fixed%20amount%20every%20month.%20The%20pot%20is%20doled%20out%20to%20one%20investor%20a%20month%20until%20everyone%20has%20received%20a%20share.%20The%20money%20is%20used%20for%20farm%20equipment%2C%20school%20fees%20or%20other%20large%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Thyagarajan%20set%20up%20other%20firms%2C%20and%20Shriram%20eventually%20grew%20into%20a%20group%20of%20more%20than%2030%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20truck%20financing%2C%20Thyagarajan%20saw%20people%20paying%20rates%20as%20steep%20as%2080%25%20because%20banks%20wouldn't%20deal%20with%20them.%20He%20concluded%20that%20the%20prevailing%20thinking%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20used%20to%20think%20that%20because%20the%20interest%20rates%20were%20very%20high%2C%20the%20lending%20was%20very%20risky%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20it%20was%20not%20risky%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%224cr7sod8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F4cr7sod8_shriram-group-structure-bloomberg_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20epiphany%20would%20define%20his%20life.%20He%20decided%20to%20lend%20at%20rates%20that%20were%20still%20extremely%20high%20by%20global%20standards%2C%20but%20lower%20than%20other%20options.%20%26quot%3BInterest%20rates%20went%20from%2030%25-35%25%20to%2017%25-18%25%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThyagarajan%20says%20his%20approach%20wasn't%20about%20charity.%20It%20was%20infused%20with%20two%20key%20capitalist%20beliefs.%20One%20was%20the%20importance%20of%20private-sector%20entrepreneurship%3B%20the%20other%2C%20faith%20in%20market%20principles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20ethos%20has%20paid%20dividends%3A%20Shriram%20collects%20more%20than%2098%25%20of%20dues%20on%20time%2C%20filings%20show.%20It%20gets%20its%20lending%20decisions%20right%2C%20the%20local%20unit%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20Ratings%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20broadly%2C%20non-bank%20financiers%20like%20Shriram%20are%20crucial%20for%20supporting%20India's%20newly%20banked.%20They%20underwrite%20loans%20and%20other%20products%20that%20require%20skill-sets%20banks%20often%20don't%20have%2C%20according%20to%20Bindu%20Ananth%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Dvara%20Holdings%2C%20which%20backs%20companies%20driving%20financial%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnsuring%20participation%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20marginalized%20in%20India's%20formal%20financial%20system%20is%20key%20to%20driving%20the%20economic%20growth%20in%20a%20sustainable%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20Ananth%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22paqrg46%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fpaqrg46_shriram-finance-office-bloomberg_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShriram%20Finance%20Ltd.%2C%20the%20flagship%2C%20has%20a%20market%20value%20of%20about%20%248.5%20billion%20and%20made%20about%20%24200%20million%20in%20profit%20in%20the%20quarter%20that%20ended%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Shriram%20Group%20serves%20about%2023%20million%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShriram%20Finance%20Ltd.%2C%20the%20flagship%2C%20has%20a%20market%20value%20of%20about%20%248.5%20billion%20and%20made%20about%20%24200%20million%20in%20profit%20in%20the%20quarter%20that%20ended%20in%20June.%20Only%20one%20of%20the%2034%20analysts%20tracking%20the%20stock%20recommends%20selling%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Different%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELending%20to%20the%20poor%20can%20be%20murky.%20Exorbitant%20interest%20rates%20routinely%20lead%20vulnerable%20borrowers%20deeper%20into%20debt.%20In%20India%2C%20loan%20sharks%20sometimes%20resort%20to%20heavy-handed%20debt%20collection.%20Consum