.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22tsev9e3o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftsev9e3o_shriram-group-headquarters-chennai-bloomberg_625x300_09_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20Shriram%20Group%20headquarters%20in%20Chennai%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Shriram%20Transport%20Finance%20Co.%20absorbed%20Shriram%20Capital%20Ltd.%20and%20Shriram%20City%20Union%20Finance%20Ltd.%20in%20a%20share-swap%20deal.%20Shriram%20Transport%20finances%20trucks%2C%20while%20Shriram%20City%20Union%20funds%20purchases%20of%20consumer%20goods%20and%20motorcycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThyagarajan%20says%20executives%20planned%20this%20for%20years%2C%20but%20he%20wasn't%20involved%20in%20the%20details.%20He%20no%20longer%20has%20a%20formal%20role%20at%20the%20company%2C%20but%20every%20fortnight%2C%20senior%20managers%20brief%20him%20and%20seek%20his%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20personality%20of%20a%20consultant%2C%26quot%3B%20Thyagarajan%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20things%20slightly%20differently.%20I'm%20OK%20with%20people%20not%20accepting%20my%20perception%20and%20doing%20things%20based%20on%20their%20perception.%20And%20if%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20I%20was%20right%20and%20they%20were%20wrong%2C%20which%20happens%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20communicate%20with%20them%20later%20on%20and%20say%20I%20told%20you%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShriram's%20strength%20is%20also%20its%20weakness%2C%20according%20to%20Kranthi%20Bathini%2C%20an%20equity%20strategist%20at%20WealthMills%20Securities%20Pvt.%20in%20Mumbai.%20Most%20customers%20are%20non-prime%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Basset%20quality%20and%20profitability%20underperformance%20could%20come%20at%20any%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20key-person%20risk%2C%20according%20to%20Bathini.%20With%20%26quot%3Bcultish%26quot%3B%