s%20call%2C%20back%20in%20early%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaneja%2C%2045%2C%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20the%20company%20fell%201.1%25%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20%24248.58%20as%20of%209%3A34%20a.m.%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20stock%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20so%20far%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20comes%20at%20a%20critical%20time%20for%20Tesla.%20The%20company%20is%20building%20a%20new%20factory%20in%20Mexico%20and%20preparing%20to%20bring%20its%20Cybertruck%20pickup%20to%20the%20market%20as%20it%20fends%20off%20rivals%20in%20the%20increasingly%20crowded%20EV%20market.%20Tesla%20has%20been%20cutting%20prices%20across%20its%20lineup%20to%20maintain%20its%20position%20atop%20the%20electric-car%20industry%2C%20and%20profitability%20has%20taken%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaneja%20started%20his%20career%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20graduated%20in%201999%20with%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20commerce%20from%20Delhi%20University%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile.%20He%20then%20spent%20almost%2017%20years%20at%20PricewaterhouseCoopers%2C%20Tesla's%20longtime%20accounting%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20SolarCity%20in%202016%20and%20became%20corporate%20controller.%20Tesla%20soon%20thereafter%20acquired%20the%20solar%20panel%20installer.%20The%20automaker's%20shareholders%20later%20sued%20Musk%20and%20Tesla's%20board%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20hiding%20SolarCity's%20financial%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaneja%20became%20Tesla's%20corporate%20controller%20in%20May%202018%20and%20was%20named%20chief%20accounting%20officer%20in%20March%202019.%20His%20predecessor%2C%20Dave%20Morton%2C%20had%20been%20hired%20away%20from%20Seagate%20Technology%20but%20resigned%20after%20less%20than%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnusual%20Arrangement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreg%20Selker%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20executive%20search%20firm%20Stanton%20Chase%2C%20said%20that%20the%20general%20trend%20in%20corporate%20America%20is%20to%20hire%20business-oriented%20CFOs%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20operational%20experience.%20Taneja%20came%20up%20through%20the%20auditing%20ranks%20at%20PwC%20and%20his%20two%20concurrent%20titles%20at%20Tesla%20are%20an%20unusual%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20CAO%20is%20responsible%20for%20all%20of%20the%20financial%20reporting%20-%20Taneja%20is%20really%20an%20accountant's%20accountant%2C%26quot%3B%20Selker%20said%20in%20a%20phone%20interview.%20%26quot%3BTypically%2C%20a%20CFO%20has%20a%20broader%20business%20background.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaneja%20may%20have%20been%20instrumental%20to%20Tesla's%20early%20inroads%20in%20India.%20He's%20one%20of%20the%20four%20directors%20at%20Tesla%20India%20Motors%20and%20Energy%20Private%20Ltd.%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%202021%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20according%20to%20the%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs.%20Tesla%20doesn't%20sell%20any%20EVs%20in%20India%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20owned%20about%20105%2C000%20shares%20of%20the%20company%20as%20of%20July%207%2C%20a%20stake%20that%20is%20currently%20valued%20at%20about%20%2426%20million%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20the%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%2C%20oversees%20six%20companies%3A%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter)%2C%20Boring%20Co.%2C%20Neuralink%20and%20xAI%2C%20his%20most%20recent%20venture.%20Musk's%20many%20interests%20and%20the%20competing%20demands%20for%20his%20time%20have%20long%20raised%20concerns%20about%20whether%20Tesla%20is%20too%20dependent%20on%20a%20single%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EV%20maker%20has%20just%20four%20executive%20officers%3A%20Musk%2C%20Drew%20Baglino%2C%20the%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20powertrain%20and%20energy%20engineering%3B%20Tom%20Zhu%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%2