such%20as%20Urmul%20Seemant%20Samiti%2C%20Desert%20Resource%20Centre%2C%20and%20Selco%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20the%20ship%20of%20the%20desert%20sail%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20is%20working%20to%20establish%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20net-zero%20dairy%20%E2%80%94%20wherein%20they%20collect%20milk%20from%204%2C000%20camel%2C%20sheep%2C%20and%20cow%20rearers%20in%20Bikaner%2C%20Jodhpur%2C%20Jaisalmer%2C%20and%20Nagaur%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20quality%20testing%2C%20the%20collected%20milk%20is%20stored%20in%20instant%20milk%20chillers%20that%20are%20claimed%20to%20bring%20the%20temperature%20down%20to%20four%20degrees%20within%20three%20minutes.%20With%20a%20storage%20capacity%20of%20500%20litres%2C%20these%20solar-powered%20milk%20chillers%20are%20installed%20in%20eight%20remote%20locations%20in%20Bikaner%20and%20Jodhpur%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1691499071.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20is%20empowering%204%2C000%20camel%2C%20sheep%2C%20and%20cow%20rearers%20in%20Bikaner%2C%20Jodhpur%2C%20Jaisalmer%2C%20and%20Nagaur%20districts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1691499071.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1691499071-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1691499071-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1691499071-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1691499071-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%