Jagtap%2C%20who%20led%20the%20229-member%20delegation%2C%20said%20they%20were%20assured%20by%20Pawar%20that%20he%20will%20not%20side%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20for%20the%20party%20without%20getting%20confused%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpune%2Fwont-join-hands-with-bjp-sharad-pawar-assures-ncps-pune-unit-amid-confusion-among-party-workers-8882392%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NCP%20chief%20has%20assured%20that%20he%20would%20be%20holding%20a%20rally%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August%20in%20Pune%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20party%20workers%20and%20citizens%20on%20his%20political%20stand.%20He%20clarified%20to%20us%20that%20he%20will%20not%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jagtap%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawar%20Senior%20also%20reportedly%20told%20the%20visiting%20delegation%20that%20BJP%20is%20trying%20hard%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20party%20and%20its%20symbol%20are%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20assured%20them%20that%20he%20will%20not%20let%20the%20saffron%20party%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawar%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%20has%20lately%20created%20confusion%20not%20just%20among%20NCP%20workers%20but%20also%20among%20the%2026-party%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%20At%20an%20event%20held%20in%20Pune%20on%20August%201%2C%20the%20NCP%20patriarch%20shared%20the%20stage%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20The%20event%20was%20held%20to%20confer%20Modi%20with%20an%20award%20instituted%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20freedom%20fighter%20Lokmanya%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak.%20Despite%20INDIA%20parties%20objecting%20Pawar%20from%20sharing%20the%20stage%20with%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20at%20a%20time%20the%20opposition%20parties%20are%20forging%20an%20alliance%20and%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20P