able-children-fashion-brand-khudey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20with%20rag%20pickers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20collect%20and%20bring%20bottles%20to%20us%2C%20for%20which%20we%20pay%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20and%20Madhuri%20have%20a%20network%20of%20more%20than%20150%20ragpickers%20in%20and%20around%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20collected%20bottles%20are%20sanitised%2C%20and%20then%20a%20rough%20design%20is%20made.%20We%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20into%20what%20can%20be%20made%20out%20of%20these%20bottles.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20people%20to%20just%20view%20them%20as%20pieces%20of%20decor.%20We%20want%20to%20promote%20the%20reuse%20of%20products%2C%20so%20we%20make%20utility%20items%20like%20platters%20and%20bowls%20out%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhuri%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20firmly%20believes%20that%20upcycling%20is%20the%20way%20forward%20and%20wants%20more%20businesses%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzrPPOhBpG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzrPPOhBpG%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdi