691155506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-1-1691153646.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noida-based%20Madhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%20started%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20creative%20way%20of%20saving%20glass%20bottles%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills.%20They%20collect%20bottles%20from%20ragpickers%20and%20customers%20and%20transform%20them%20into%20functional%20art%20items.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326377%2Fnoida-madhuri-balodi-amit-singh-kavi-the-poetry-art-project-glass-bottle-art-sustainability-home-decor%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20to%20Expect%20at%20COP28%20UAE%3A%20A%20Global%20Movement%20to%20Fight%20Climate%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EClimate%20action%20requires%20the%20collaboration%20and%20cooperation%20of%20individuals%2C%20communities%2C%20organisations%2C%20and%20governments.%20And%20to%20mitigate%20its%20effects%2C%20we%20need%20to%20shift%20from%20incremental%20steps%20to%20transformational%20progress%20that%20delivers%20for%20everyone%2C%20everywhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20exactly%20what%20COP28%20will%20seek%20to%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20COP%20and%20why%20is%20it%20important%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20is%20the%20supreme%20decision-making%20body%20for%20all%20States%20that%20are%20Parties%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Framework%20Convention%20on%20Climate%20Change%20(UNFCCC).%20The%20UNFCCC%20came%20into%20force%20on%2021%20March%201994%20with%20the%20aim%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20prevent%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%E2%80%9D%20human%20interference%20with%20the%20climate%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20COP%20meets%20every%20year%20to%20assess%20the%20progress%20that%20has%20been%20made%20towards%20this.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20meetings%20have%20resulted%20in%20several%20legally%20binding%20international%20agreements%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20including%20the%202015%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%20well%20below%202%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20pre-industrial%20levels%20and%20pursue%20efforts%20to%20limit%20the%20temperature%20increase%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECOP28%20UAE%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028th%20COP%20is%20being%20hosted%20by%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20at%20Expo%20City%20Dubai%20between%2030%20November%20and%2012%20December%202023.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20COP%20of%20unity%2C%20solidarity%2C%20and%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOP28%20will%20see%20the%20first%20Global%20Stocktake%20(GST)%2C%20a%20process%20mandated%20by%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20to%20evaluate%20advancements%20towards%20its%20objectives.%20It%20is%20against%20this%20backdrop%20that%20COP28%20will%20bring%20everyone%20to%20the%20table%20to%20recalibrate%2C%20raise%20ambitions%20and%20maximise%20the%20opportunities%20of%20the%20clean%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20UAE%20hosted%20the%20annual%20Abu%20Dhabi%20Sustainability%20Week%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286865%2Feasy-steps-to-be-sustainable-at-home-no-plastic-use-save-money-sustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20established%20in%202008%20to%20accelerate%20sustainable%20economic%20development%20and%20facilitate%20partnerships%20to%20enable%20the%20energy%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20XX%20edition%20of%20ADSW%20drove%20momentum%20between%20COP27%20and%20COP28%2C%20enabling%20impactful%20and%20continuous%20dialogue%20between%20key%20stakeholders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20was%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20region%20to%20announce%20its%20commitment%20to%20Net%20Zero%20and%20has%20a%20proud%20track%20record%20of%20investing%20in%20the%20energy%20transition.%20This%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271708%2Fstartup-innovation-convert-renewable-energy-water-uravu-labs-bengaluru-engineer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%20powerhouse%2C%20Masdar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Climate%20Leadership%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMasdar%20was%20established%20in%202006%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UAE%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20vision%20to%20diversify%20its%20economy%20and%20bring%20about%20a%20cycle%20of%20growth%20and%20innovation.%20His%20Excellency%20Dr%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%2C%20the%20COP%20President%20Designate%2C%20is%20Masdar%E2%80%99s%20founding%20CEO%20and%20current%20Chairman.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20company%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20investors%20in%20renewable%20energy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Masdar%20has%20a%20combined%20investment%20portfolio%20valued%20at%20%2430bn.%20It%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20climate%20innovation%2C%20operating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287058%2Frenewable-energy-map-india-wind-power-plants-project-largest-solar-park-environment-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20renewable%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20