C%20cutting%20boards%2C%20compostable%20bags%2C%20etc%20in%20December%202022.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20we%20sell%20in%20India%20is%20made%20in%20India.%20India%20is%20our%20next%20big%20bet.%20We%20are%20already%20available%20online%20and%20are%20now%20planning%20to%20launch%20in%2010%2C000%20stores%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20products%20are%20priced%20anywhere%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%20200%20to%20Rs%20800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20using%20sustainable%20products%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20It%20is%20during%20the%20search%20for%20such%20products%20that%20I%20came%20across%20EcoSoul.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20using%20their%20palm%20leaf%20plates%20and%20dinnerware%20sets.%20They%20are%20great%20for%20parties.%20I%20like%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20compostable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonia%2C%20a%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20mistakes%20on%20their%20own%20dime%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsqopbTJZfo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsqopbTJZfo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsqopbTJZfo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20EcoSoul%20Home%20India%20(%40ecosoul_ind)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20bootstrapped%20for%20the%20first%2014%20months%20of%20the%20business%2C%20their%20first%20investor%20was%20a%20retailer.%20%E2%80%9COur%20first%20retailer%20was%20enthused%20by%20our%20product%E2%80%99s%20performance.%20He%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20he%20cut%20us%20a%20%241%2C00%2C000%20cheque.%20We%20had%20approached%20various%20VCs%20(venture%20capitals)%20but%20no%20one%20was%20willing%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20sustainability%20space%20then.%20We%20were%20so%20happy%20when%20a%20retailer%20invested%20in%20us%2C%20which%20is%20rare%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomer%20reviews%20also%20buoyed%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20all%20in.%20I%20had%20sold%20my%20house%2C%20Arvind%20had%20sold%20his%20shares%2C%20and%20we%20exhausted%20our%20savings.%20When%20we%20saw%20a%20repeat%20purchase%20rate%20of%20more%20than%2030%20percent%2C%20we%20were%20ecstatic.%20It%20was%20the%20silver%20lining%20for%20us.%20Reading%20positive%20reviews%20about%20the%20quality%20felt%20great%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%E2%80%99%2015%2B%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20big%20banks%20and%20corporates%2C%20combined%20with%20their%20bootstrapped%20approach%2C%20provided%20them%20with%20valuable%20discipline%20and%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%2040-year-olds%2C%20we%20have%20helped%20scale%20many%20companies%20and%20products.%20We%20used%20this%20experience%20and%20maturity%20when%20we%20started%20our%20business.%20It%20was%20a%20calculated%20risk.%20Not%20getting%20investment%2C%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20was%20actually%20a%20blessing%20for%20us.%20We%20built%20a%20business%20model%20that%20was%20inherently%20profitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20advises%20budding%20entrepreneurs%20not%20to%20be%20swayed%20by%20the%20allure%20of%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20thinks%20that%20starting%20your%20own%20company%20is%20glamorous.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not.%20There%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20having%20a%20regular%20nine-to-five%20job.%20And%20even%20when%20you%20decide%20to%20start%20out%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20build%20a%20company%20that%20survives%20on%20VC%20money.%20That%20is%20a%20dangerous%20business%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Priyanka%20Aeron%2C%20India%20Managing%20Director%20and%20Head%20of%20Global%20HR%20%26amp%3B%20Tech%2C%20swears%20by%20the%20philosophy%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20inherit%20the%20earth%20from%20our%20parents%3B%20we%20borrow%20it%20from%20our%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20extensive%20range%20of%20home%20essentials%20embraces%20our%20idea%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20own%20the%20Earth.%20We%20are%20merely%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325564%2Fthe-disposal-company-bhagyashree-bhansali-waste-plastic-credit-recycle-mumbai-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eborrowing%20it%20from%20the%20future%20generation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20the%20long%20haul%2C%20easier%20yet%20impactful%20changes%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20altering%20our%20carbon%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20explore%20their%20sustainable%20products%2C%20you%20can%20visit%20the%20official%20website%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fecosoulhome.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Rahul%20Singh%2C%20EcoSoul%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691070457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fecosoul-1691067035.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326200%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Entrepreneurs%20Rahul%20Singh%20and%20Arvind%20Ganesan%20started%20EcoSoul%20Home%20to%20provide%20sustainable%20alternatives%20to%20single-use%20plastic.%20With%20tableware%20made%20of%20palm%20leaf%20and%20sugarcane%20bagasse%2C%20they%20have%20now%20built%20a%20business%20on%20track%20to%20clock%20%2450%20million%20in%20revenue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98They%20Call%20it%20a%20Man%E2%80%99s%20Job%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Lives%20%26%20Tribulations%20of%204%20Women%20Who%20Cremate%20Unclaimed%20Bodies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20Warning%3A%20Graphic%20mentions%20of%20death%2C%20blood%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20when%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Madhusmita%20Prusty%20was%20leaving%20for%20work%20at%208%3A30%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20Government%20Railway%20Police%20(GRP).%20It%20was%20to%20inform%20her%20about%20the%20unfortunate%20Odisha%20triple%20train%20accident%2C%20which%20had%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20295%20passengers%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%20the%20previous%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20noon%20on%20June%203%2C%20the%20Bhubneswar%20resident%20reached%20Balasore%20along%20with%20three%20other%20women%20%E2%80%94%20Smita%20Mohanty%2C%20Swagatika%20Rao%2C%20and%20Snehanjali%20Sethi%20%E2%80%94%20in%20their%20ambulance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20episode%2C%20Madhusmita%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20there%20was%20very%20unsettling.%20Blood%20was%20everywhere.%20Some%20were%20lying%20without%20limbs.%20The%20injured%20were%20crying%20for%20help.%20If%20we%20carried%20somebody%20to%20take%20them%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20others%20would%20insist%20that%20we%20take%20them%20first.%20It%20was%20so%20hard%20for%20us%2C%20we%20did%20not%20know%20where%20to%20begin.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20emotional%20state%20for%20us.%20Their%20cries%20still%20echo%20in%20our%20ears.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Madhusmita%20was%20joined%20by%20Smita%2C%20Swagatika%2C%20and%20Snehanjali%20in%20the%20initiative.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305.jpeg%201040w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-31-at-12.48.53-AM-1691066305-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326203%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMadhusmita%20is%20joined%20by%20Smita%2C%20Swagatika%2C%20and%20Snehanjali%20in%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20women%20were%20called%20to%20help%20the%20administration%20in%20transporting%20the%20injured%20to%20the%20hospitals%20and%20cremating%20unidentified%20and%20unclaimed%20bodies.%20%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20situation%2C%20we%20first%20focussed%20on%20admitting%20severely%20injured%20people%20to%20hospitals%20in%20Cuttack%20and%20Balasore.%20Later%2C%20we%20were%20permitted%20to%20cremate%20five%20bodies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20many%20as%2029%20bodies%20are%20still%20preserved%20in%20AIIMS%2C%20Bhubaneswar%20premises%20to%20be%20identified%20by%20the%20authorities.%20After%20receiving%20the%20final%20round%20of%20DNA%20cross-matching%20reports%2C%20the%20authorities%20may%20conduct%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126580%2Fcremation-wood-green-alternatives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emass%20cremation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20unidentified%20bodies.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20is%20ongoing%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20identification%20of%20the%20dead.%20We%20might%20soon%20be%20called%20to%20cremate%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECourage%20above%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20Madhusmita%20was%20working%20with%20a%20Kolkata%20hospital%20as%20a%20nurse%20in%20the%20paediatrics%20department.%20Over%20her%2015%20year%20career%2C%20she%20often%20saw%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20see%20wailing%20children%20and%20elderly%20next%20to%20their%20loved%20ones.%20They%20would%20not%20have%20sufficient%20money%20to%20perform%20the%20last%20rites%20and%20the%20authorities%20demanded%20a%20huge%20amount%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remembered%20how%20my%20husband%20%5Bwh