non-profit%20has%20assisted%20more%20than%204%2C000%20migrant%20children%20from%20states%20like%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Assam%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20in%20joining%20mainstream%20schools%20without%20any%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20handhold%20them%20right%20from%20their%20schooling%20to%20college%20enrollment.%20Our%20dream%20is%20to%20see%20all%20children%2C%20like%20Vijay%2C%20get%20into%20good%20universities.%20When%20impoverished%20families%20move%20to%20new%20states%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20feel%20secure%20and%20cared%20for.%20Every%20child%20deserves%20a%20complete%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manimakalai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Gubbachi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690982300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-2-1690981282.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20happens%20when%20families%20migrate%20in%20search%20of%20jobs%3F%20Their%20children%20miss%20out%20on%20education.%20But%20six%20Bengaluru%20friends%20and%20their%20enterprise%20Gubbachi%20are%20working%20to%20ensure%20their%20educational%20inclusion%20for%20free.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326013%2Fbengaluru-friends-run-gubacchi-non-profit-to-educate-migrant-worker-children-for-free%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Moms%20Serve%20the%20Magic%20of%20Home-Cooked%2C%20Eco-Friendly%20%E2%80%98Dabbas%E2%80%99%20to%20Thousands%20in%20London%C2%A0%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20object%20that%20ties%20two%20strangers%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lunchbox%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2013)%20is%20the%20ubiquitous%20%3Cem%3Edabba%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20rare%20mix-up%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabbawalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20what%20leads%20Ila%20(Nimrat%20Kaur%20and%20Saajan%20(Irffan%20Khan)%20to%20develop%20a%20special%20bond%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecomes%20a%20medium%20through%20which%20they%20express%20themselves%20and%20their%20desires.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20every%20Indian%20household%2C%20where%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20cabinets%20full%20of%20various%20steel%2C%20plastic%2C%20glass%2C%20and%20tupperware%20containers.%20In%20school%20and%20college%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300680%2Fdublin-cloud-kitchen-o-desi-meals-delivers-authentic-indian-food-helps-homeless%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopening%20the%20dabba%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20way%20to%20forge%20friendships%20and%20share%20pieces%20of%20our%20lives%20wrapped%20in%20the%20food.%20How%20many%20times%20have%20we%20heard%2C%20or%20asked%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAaj%20dabbe%20main%20kya%20hai%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(What%E2%80%99s%20in%20your%20dabba%20today%3F)%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong-time%20neighbours%20and%20friends%20Anshu%20Ahuja%20and%20Renee%20Williams%2C%20too%2C%20find%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20their%20dreams.%20In%202018%2C%20they%20started%20Dabba%20Drop%2C%20and%20Anshu%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20starting%20an%20eco-friendly%20delivery%20business%20was%20the%20waste%20that%20gets%20accumulated%20when%20we%20order%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20people%20have%20started%20ordering%20a%20lot%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20arrival%20of%20food%20delivery%20apps.%20After%20having%20that%20food%2C%20we%20end%20up%20with%20a%20bin%20full%20of%20plastic.%20The%20packaging%20is%20very%20wasteful%20and%20greasy.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20recycle%20it.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20better%20way%20to%20order%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anshu%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20a%20Tamilian%20mother%20and%20Punjabi%20father%2C%20food%20was%20a%20big%20part%20of%20her%20life%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20my%20favourite%20food%20when%20we%20would%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20was%20%3Cem%3Epav%20bhaji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20chinese.%20When%20I%E2%80%99d%20get%20home%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20try%20to%20recreate%20those%20dishes.%20This%20way%20I%20could%20continue%20to%20taste%20the%20flavours.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20childhood%20in%20Mumbai%20meant%20that%20Anshu%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabbawalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20have%20been%20serving%20food%20to%20over%202%20lakh%20people%20daily%20since%201890.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20mix%20of%20love%20for%20home-cooked%20food%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabbawala%20institution%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20led%20her%20to%20quit%20her%2015-year-long%20career%20as%20a%20TV%20producer%20in%20East%20London%20to%20start%20Dabba%20Drop%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20theatre%20of%20the%20humble%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Edabba%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20menu%20of%20the%20dabba%20changes%20weekly%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-4-1690980243-500x262.j