%3ETo%20crack%20the%20NEET%20exam%2C%20most%20of%20the%20aspirants%20turn%20towards%20coaching%20and%20private%20assistance.%20But%20for%20Umer%2C%20that%20was%20not%20an%20option.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20take%20any%20coaching%20because%20of%20two%20reasons.%20One%2C%20I%20could%20not%20afford%20them%2C%20and%20two%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20spare%20the%20time%20to%20attend%20extra%20classes%20while%20I%20juggled%20school%20and%20labour.%20Instead%2C%20I%20used%20the%20internet%20and%20NCERT%20to%20crack%20the%20paper%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20resources%20online%2C%20he%20found%20some%20helpful%20lectures%20on%20YouTube.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20found%20a%20free%20lecture%20online%20by%20Physics%20Wallah%20and%20then%20decided%20to%20take%20that%20course.%20It%20was%20for%20Rs%203%2C500%2C%20which%20I%20could%20afford.%20That%20helped%20me%20a%20lot%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmer%20shares%20these%20tips%20for%20future%20aspirants%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20important%20thing%20that%20every%20aspirant%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20is%20to%20learn%20everything%20that%20the%20NCERT%20books%20offer.%20Many%20times%2C%20aspirants%20focus%20only%20on%20the%20notes%20got%20from%20coaching%20classes%2C%20but%20that%20will%20not%20cover%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CFocus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300235%2Fupsc-cse-prelim-where-you-can-get-ncert-books-free-download%2F%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20you%20will%20easily%20get%20good%20marks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20advises%20them%20to%20revise%20everything.%20%E2%80%9CMake%20thorough%20notes%20and%20bullet%20points.%20Then%20keep%20revising%20them%20so%20everything%20remains%20fresh%20in%20your%20head.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledges%20that%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam%20can%20be%20stressful.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20one%